    {
        "role": "assistant",
        "content": "### Business Summary\nyeh rakham ki maloomat hai ke F.B.AREA BLOCK-3 ne sab se zada **Internal Units Sold** kiya hai, jiska **Sales** quantity 783,091 hai.\n### Key Highlights\n* **Product Name:** F.B.AREA BLOCK-3\n* **Quantity Sold:** 783,091\n* **Highest Sales** wala product hai\n### Insight\nyeh Company ke **Growth** ke liye acha hai ke woh apne **Sales** strategy ko aur bhi behetr banaye, ta ke **Business** ko aur bhi zada **Profit** hasil ho.",
        "sql": "WITH Internal AS (\n  SELECT ib.name, SUM(ms.product_quantity) as qty \n  FROM master_sale ms \n  JOIN customer_details cd ON ms.customer_id = cd.customer_id \n  JOIN ims_brick ib ON cd.ims_brick_id = ib.id \n  GROUP BY 1\n)\nSELECT name, qty \nFROM Internal \nORDER BY qty DESC \nLIMIT 1;",
